@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ipvssx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.21 + v2 + 0.91)) * 0.55)
    v1 = v0
    v2 = wp.sin((wp.abs(v0 + 0.57) + wp.cos(v2 + 0.30)))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.exp(wp.abs(v1 + 0.80)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v2 + 0.28)) / wp.abs((v1 + 0.10 * v2 + 0.54)))
    v2 = (0.43 + (wp.sin(tmp + 0.41) + wp.sin(v2 + 0.10)))
    v0 = wp.abs((0.91 - wp.exp(v0 + 0.62)))
    data[tid] = v0
